{"tid":1848200,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"HA真係史上最有良心嘅僱主呀！","createTime":"2020-01-28T10:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T12:26:50.000Z","uid":40184,"like":983,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"a02394aeec2f9be08517d8a52bead7b82688b89f","tid":1848200,"uid":40184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:38:33.000Z","msg":"*💁🏻&zwj;♀醫院管理局總辦事處訊息：*<br />\n<br />\n公立醫院已經啓動緊急應變級別，全體同事都肩負重任，全力抗疫。<br />\n因此，假期後所有同事都須繼續緊守崗位執勤。<br />\n衷心感謝各同事維持服務運作，攜手守護市民健康。🙏🏻🙏🏻🙏🏻<br />\n<br />\n*💁🏻&zwj;♀Message from HAHO:*<br />\nWith the activation of Emergency Response Level in public hospitals, all colleagues are required to report duty after the holiday. <br />\nYour contributions and dedication are much appreciated! ❤❤❤<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母</span>啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我淨係想平平安安健健康康咋！<br />\n關你又唔撚封，仲要我返工？<br />\n如果我殉職，我條命仲要值得嗰三十萬？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係一年人工都高撚過你呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢份工我真係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔撚返</span>呀！<br />\n一月二九，罷你老母！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ede3be05c67bf9f4f936dcbcf748575038ee00","tid":1848200,"uid":258696,"like":131,"dislike":1,"score":130,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:40:31.000Z","msg":"罷工手足勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n炸彈手足型<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b9068ee941be18bd4b714d12d0fe2358a7a883","tid":1848200,"uid":181549,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:40:45.000Z","m